The paper discusses the topic of explainable artificial intelligence (XAI) and proposes a reasoning model to explain a neural network's decision. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of AI (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing (NLP) techniques to produce explanations, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and systems and control (cs.SY).
